FT  05 DEC 94 / Observer: Frontiersmen
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Oh, the perils of those otherwise seductive emerging markets. The Dollars
50m Vietnam Frontier Fund, which has Bangkok merchant bank Finansa Thai
controlling 70 per cent of its management company, was minded to throw a big
bash for the opening of its Hanoi office.
Out went the invitations to the great and the good, whereupon the Vietnamese
